Richmond

Julia F. Boswell v. Roy H. Boswell. April 28, 1969. Record No. 6864. Present, Eggleston, C.J., and Buchanan, I’Anson, Carrico, Gordon and Harrison, JJ. Harry P. Anderson, Jr. (William Patrick Coleman; Satterfield, Haw, Anderson, Parkerson & Beazley, on brief), for the appellant. R. B. Stephenson, Jr. (Stephenson, Kostel, Watson & Carson, on brief), for the appellee.

Decree affirmed without opinion by equally divided Court.
